OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,FThe infant sleep industry has become a
OL,8,F"Wild West" with new parents being
OL,9,Fgiven incorrect information by
OL,10,F"dangerous" individuals posing as
OL,11,Fexperts, a North West Labour MP has
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FConnor Rand said self-proclaimed
OL,15,Fprofessionals are able to "give
OL,16,Fparents advice that puts their child's
OL,17,Flife at risk" without any consequences.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]rD@AOUrD@KO]wD@[OUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,FA four-month old baby in his
OL,8,FAltrincham and Sale West constituency
OL,9,Fdied after being put into an unsafe
OL,10,Fsleeping position on the advice of
OL,11,Fsomeone who called themselves a
OL,12,Fmaternity nurse, despite having no
OL,13,Fmedical qualifications.
OL,15,FIn the case of Madison Bruce Smith,
OL,16,Fthe grandson of football manager Steve
OL,17,FBruce, senior coroner Alison Mutch
OL,18,Fissued a prevention of future deaths
OL,19,Freport to the Secretary of State for
OL,20,FHealth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,FThe Government has pledged to protect
OL,8,Fthe title of "nurse" within this
OL,9,FParliament and will publish a call for
OL,10,Fevidence "shortly", health minister
OL,11,FKarin Smyth told the Commons on Monday.
OL,13,FMr Rand pressed for this legislation
OL,14,Fto go further and include titles such
OL,15,Fas "practitioner" and "consultant", to
OL,16,Fprotect vulnerable parents.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@TO]rD@JOUrD@RO]wD@DOUwD@QO]wD@
OL,26,AWOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,FHe also said mandatory training and
OL,8,Fstandards, in addition to a national
OL,9,Fregister, for those providing home-
OL,10,Fbased childcare would "strengthen
OL,11,Fsafeguarding", give parents clarity
OL,12,Fand professionalise the sector.
OL,14,FMr Rand told MPs: "Health visitors and
OL,15,Fthe vast majority of nannies who
OL,16,Fprovide responsible care give us vital
OL,17,Fsupport that helps parents get by.
OL,26,@rD@WOUsD@MO]vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,F"But what if when we turned for help
OL,8,Fthe person who responded was not
OL,9,Fsomeone we could trust? What if they
OL,10,Fwere not the expert they claimed or
OL,11,Fseemed to be? What if they had no
OL,12,Fqualifications, no training and no
OL,13,Faccountability?
OL,15,F"When this happens, we run the risk of
OL,16,Funimaginable tragedy."
OL,18,FHe added: "The support we used to
OL,19,Fprovide for new parents has shrunk. In
OL,20,Fthe gaps that this has caused, the
OL,21,Finfant sleep industry has boomed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUxD@VO]zD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,F"And this industry is a Wild West
OL,8,Fwhere literally anyone can pose as an
OL,9,Fexpert and give parents advice that
OL,10,Fputs their child's life at risk."
OL,12,FHe added: "People looking after
OL,13,Fchildren should have basic medical and
OL,14,Fearly years training, including on
OL,15,Fsafe sleep.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@aO]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,F"This change could introduce standards
OL,8,Fand safeguards to an industry badly
OL,9,Flacking in both and it supports the
OL,10,Fmajority of people who provide
OL,11,Fresponsible home-based care for
OL,12,Fchildren while cracking down on the
OL,13,Fdangerous minority who don't.
OL,15,F"It gives parents peace of mind and
OL,16,Fminimum legal standards to hold
OL,17,Fproviders against.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,F"And the introduction of mandatory
OL,8,Ftraining and standards could lead to
OL,9,Fthe development of a national
OL,10,Fregulated framework or register for
OL,11,Fall those providing home-based
OL,12,Fchildcare.
OL,14,F"With a register, we strengthen
OL,15,Fsafeguarding, give parents clarity and
OL,16,Fprofessionalise the sector."
OL,18,FResponding to the debate, Ms Smyth
OL,19,Facknowledged the public is being
OL,20,Fmisled by those in the industry.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,FShe said the use of titles can give
OL,8,Fthe "impression that such individuals
OL,9,Fare qualified and professionally
OL,10,Fregistered to provide a particular
OL,11,Flevel of care advice or care
OL,12,Fintervention that they do not hold,
OL,13,Fwhich puts the public and babies at
OL,14,Frisk".
OL,26,@pD@EOUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,F"Protecting the title nurse will make
OL,8,Fit a criminal offence for someone to
OL,9,Fcall themselves a nurse unless they
OL,10,Fare registered as a nurse with the
OL,11,FNursing and Midwifery Council, or part
OL,12,Fof one of a number of exempt
OL,13,Fprofessions, such as dental nurses and
OL,14,Fveterinary nurses.
OL,16,F"And these new protections will apply
OL,17,Fto longer professional titles that
OL,18,Finclude the word nurse, such as
OL,19,Fmaternity nurse and night nurse," she
OL,20,Fadded.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1781002969
OL,3,CBabies lives could be put at risk
OL,4,Cunless sleep industry is urgently
OL,5,Cregulated
OL,7,FMs Smyth said all early years
OL,8,Fproviders are required to meet the
OL,9,Fsafer sleep requirements set out in
OL,10,Fthe statutory framework.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
